rows.label: xs06110170_MSG0002
rows.name:
Commander Vandham,
what are you doing here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06110170_MSG0004
rows.name: Lin, I was waiting for you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06110170_MSG0006
rows.name: You're interested, right? In that unit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06110170_MSG0008
rows.name: In that case, I'll leave the investigation of that unit to you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06110170_MSG0009
rows.name:
Recovering that unit was your[ST:wide ]―
No, your team's accomplishment after all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06110170_MSG0011
rows.name:
Preparations are already done.
Get inside, quickly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06110170_MSG0012
rows.name:
Okay, thank you very much,
Commander Vandham![ST:wait ]
